      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly and dependable daily driver? This vehicle is in fair condition, showing some honest character and signs of use from its years of reliable service, but it\u2019s still ready to get you where you need to go! It\u2019s a great opportunity to own a functional car that still has plenty of miles left in it at a fantastic price.",
