      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is best suited for someone looking for a dependable daily driver who isn't concerned with cosmetic perfection. The exterior shows several noticeable scratches, some minor door dings, and fading paint on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and some staining, though all electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it does have the expected rattles and road noise of a high-mileage vehicle. It is a solid, honest car that will get you where you need to go without any surprises.",
