    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a buyer looking for a major project or a parts donor. The exterior has significant rust on the rocker panels and several large dents, while the interior shows heavy wear with torn seats and a failing headliner. Mechanically, the engine has a persistent knock and the transmission shifts harshly, so it will likely need a full overhaul to be reliable again.",
