      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it's completely spotless inside and out. You really won't find one in better condition. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
