    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six power plant. This example boasts a lightning-fast throttle response courtesy of its individual throttle bodies and a precision-gated Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. The limited-slip differential operates with factory-spec lockup, and the suspension geometry remains true, delivering the quintessential analog driving experience. Finished in a concours-level coat with zero clear coat failure, this is a mechanically sorted, collector-grade specimen for the uncompromising enthusiast.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
