    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to a standard that rivals its first day on the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, preserved by climate-controlled storage and a recent ceramic coating. Inside, the premium leather seats remain supple and completely free of any creasing or wear, while the cabin retains that distinct new-car scent. Every button, switch, and technological feature operates with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach; the engine runs silently, and the transmission shifts with seamless fluidity. Accompanied by a complete, documented service history from the original purchase date, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or discerning enthusiast to own a truly flawless example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
